'''Thunderbird''' is Mozilla's solution to the e-mail client.

'''Earlybird''' is the "unbranded" version of Thunderbird.

== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=mail-client/thunderbird}}

=== Emerge ===

{{Emerge|mail-client/thunderbird}}

Emerging Thunderbird is a long process, a pre-compiled (binary) version exists for users who want a shorter install time:

{{Emerge|mail-client/thunderbird-bin}}

Note that behavior of the pre-compiled version may be different in many ways including the choice of default applications for URLs.

== Configuration ==

=== XDG integration ===

To ensure Thunderbird is being used by other applications for handling <code>mailto:</code> links, run:

{{Cmd|xdg-mime default thunderbird.desktop x-scheme-handler/mailto}}

== Usage ==

=== Keyboard shortcuts ===

Thunderbird has a variety of keyboard shortcuts built-in. A full listing can be viewed on the [https://support.mozilla.org/t5/Tips-and-Tricks/Keyboard-Shortcuts-TB/ta-p/13987 Mozilla support page].

